When you select a date variable, Einstein displays a chart with the date variable along the horizontal axis.

Chart Axes
Horizontal - Explanatory Variable (date) for this insight. Sorted chronologically from left to right.
Vertical - Outcome Variable for this model.

Hover-Over Details
Total - Sum of Outcome Variable for all observations that meet the Condition.
Count - Number of observations that meet the Condition.
Different from Average - The average for Condition minus the global average.
Outcome Variable - Average of Outcome Variable for all observations that meet the Condition (Sum / Count).
Global Average - Global average of all variables.
